                     <interp inst="t18480821-1825-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, stealing 1 watch, value 8<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18480821-name-319" type="victimName">
